data.description: ***Welcome HOME ***  This Beautiful, home has 4 bedrooms, 2.5 baths and 2 car garage, with a lot of upgrades! A  stunning open concept with a dining room that welcomes you into a large kitchen. Beautiful, granite counter tops and custom designed backsplash. The kitchen is open to the breakfast area and the stunning family room. The family room has a beautiful view to a floor to ceiling fire place and to the wooded back yard, it also has tons of natural light. The primary bedroom is huge an spacious, with a large bathroom (walking shower and a tub), and a huge walking closet. If that is not enough, this immaculate home is seating in 3/4 of an acre of land. Imagine the amount of projects that you could do in this amount of space.
